{"tid":218058,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電競之父鍾培生表示「想贊助谷阿莫一點律師費」","createTime":"2017-04-26T08:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T16:56:45.000Z","uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7123a6b00664025ff71022e9d4b84cc1c3189a02","tid":218058,"uid":22270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"谷阿莫快來看！有大老闆找你！<br />\n網路紅人谷阿莫著「X分鐘看完XX電影」系列影片爆紅，但日前也因此陷入侵權糾紛，網路影視平台KKTV和電影公司「又水整合」昨證實已正式對谷阿莫提出「侵權」告訴。<br />\n<br />\n事後谷阿莫堅持是「網路著作權的合理使用」，引發網路熱烈討論，香港電競公司、HKES戰隊老闆鍾培生稍早在臉書發文希望可以聯絡到谷阿莫，表示「想贊助他一點律師費」，因為「這事件沒有明確的案例可作參考，希望藉此案件了解更多台灣法例和文化。」<br />\n<br />\n有網友看完在底下留言稱讚「佛心老闆」「大哥說話了」「生哥要找人，應該也是隨便CALL就有了」，但也有網友奉勸「老闆不用幫這人吧！他用盜版片營利阿！」「別幫他，拍攝一部電影的心血心力不是他在那邊講五分鐘X話可以比擬的！」（張鈜閔／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170425/1104931/%E8%B0%B7%E9%98%BF%E8%8E%AB%E5%BF%AB%E7%9C%8B%EF%BC%81%E3%80%80%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E5%AF%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E8%A6%81%E5%B9%AB%E4%BD%A0%E5%87%BA%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170425%2F1104931%2F%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E9%2598%25BF%25E8%258E%25AB%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%259C%258B%25EF%25BC%2581%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25B2%25BB&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=61230f7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170425/1104931/%E8%B0%B7%E9%98%BF%E8%8E%AB%E5%BF%AB%E7%9C%8B%EF%BC%81%E3%80%80%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E5%AF%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E8%A6%81%E5%B9%AB%E4%BD%A0%E5%87%BA%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%B2%BB</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32x14s1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32x14s1.png&h=b24268aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9326aa225596677444750151e12e597793522fc7","tid":218058,"ui